data.comment: The first-half is just kicking off.
Ball safe as Tosu is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 1, Throw-in for Tokyo at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Tokyo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Can Tosu get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Tokyo's half?
In the minute 2, Masaaki Iemoto signals a Tokyo throw-in in Tosu's half.
Hirotaka Mita (Tokyo) wins the ball in the air but heads wide.
Tosu have a goal kick.
In the minute 4, Throw-in for Tosu in their own half.
Tosu to take a throw-in in Tokyo territory.
Tosu have been awarded a corner by Masaaki Iemoto.
In the minute 6, Free kick for Tosu in the half of Tokyo.
Masaaki Iemoto awards the away team a throw-in.
Masaaki Iemoto awards Tokyo a goal kick.
In the minute 10, Diego Oliveira (Tokyo) strikes â€“ and hits the bar! Ohhhh so close!
Tokyo's Leandro breaks free at Ajinomoto Stadium. But the strike goes wide of the post.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Tokyo.
In the minute 11, Tokyo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in Tokyo.
Tosu push upfield but Masaaki Iemoto quickly pulls them for offside.
In the minute 16, Throw-in for Tokyo in their own half.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tokyo in their own half.
Throw-in Tosu.
In the minute 21, Free kick for Tokyo in their own half.
In Tokyo a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tosu.
In the minute 24, Goal kick for Tosu at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Yuta Higuchi (Tosu) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Corner awarded to Tosu.
In the minute 29, Goal! Kaisei Ishii gives Tosu a 0-1 lead.
Great play from Yuto Uchida to set up the goal.
Tosu's Yuta Higuchi gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 31, Ball goes out of play for a Tokyo goal kick.
Free kick for Tosu in their own half.
Leandro for Tokyo has been booked by Masaaki Iemoto and receives a first yellow card.
In the minute 36, Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tokyo in their own half.
Throw-in for Tosu at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Free kick Tokyo.
In the minute 39, Leandro levels the score at 1-1.
Ball safe as Tosu is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Masaaki Iemoto awards Tosu a goal kick.
In the minute 41, Tosu awarded a free kick in their own half.
Tokyo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Masaaki Iemoto awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 43, Tokyo advance rapidly upfield but Masaaki Iemoto blows for offside.
Ryoya Morishita puts the ball in the net and the away team now lead 1-2.
Masaaki Iemoto awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 44, At Ajinomoto Stadium, Diego Oliveira has been yellow-carded for the home team.
Free kick in a good position for Tokyo!
3 minutes of injury time will be added to the 1st half.
In the minute 45, Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Masaaki Iemoto.
Throw-in for Tokyo in the half of Tosu.
Free kick for Tosu in their own half.
The first half has been concluded at Ajinomoto Stadium.
In the minute 45, Sei Muroya (Tokyo) has received a first yellow card.
Masaaki Iemoto has blown to start the second-half.
In the minute 46, Can Tokyo capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Tosu's half?
Ball safe as Tosu is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tosu.
In the minute 49, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Throw-in for Tosu in their own half.
Tokyo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 51, In Tokyo a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tosu in their own half.
Tokyo awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 54, Throw-in Tosu.
Goal kick for Tokyo at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Corner awarded to Tosu.
In the minute 56, It's now 1-3 in Tokyo as Cho Dong-geon scores for Tosu.
At Ajinomoto Stadium, Tosu are penalized for being offside.
The home team replace Leandro with Takuya Uchida.
In the minute 57, Tokyo make their second substitution with Adailton replacing Yojiro Takahagi.
Throw-in for Tosu at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Cho Dong-geon is writhing in pain and play has been suspended for a few moments.
In the minute 60, The away team has substituted Cho Dong-geon with Yohei Toyoda. Myung Hwi Kim is thus making his first change.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Corner awarded to Tokyo.
In the minute 62, Can Tokyo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Tosu's half?
Free kick for Tokyo in the half of Tosu.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Tokyo.
In the minute 64, Masaaki Iemoto signals a Tosu throw-in in Tokyo's half.
Free kick Tokyo.
Throw-in for Tokyo at Ajinomoto Stadium.
In the minute 66, Masaaki Iemoto signals a throw-in for Tokyo, close to Tosu's area.
In the minute 67, Adailton is back on the pitch.
Play has been temporarily suspended for attention to Adailton for Tokyo who is writhing in pain on the pitch.
The match has been stopped briefly for attention to the injured Teruki Hara.
Ball goes out of play for a Tosu goal kick.
Teruki Hara for Tosu is back on the field again.
Tosu to take a throw-in in Tokyo territory.
Throw-in Tokyo.
In the minute 70, Taichi Hara is replacing Kensuke Nagai for the home team.
In the minute 73, Free kick for Tosu in their own half.
An Yong-Woo is replacing Yuta Higuchi for Tosu at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Throw-in for Tosu in the half of Tokyo.
In the minute 74, Tokyo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a Tokyo throw-in in Tosu's half.
Tosu awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 76, Ball safe as Tosu is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Tokyo have been awarded a corner by Masaaki Iemoto.
Tosu have a goal kick.
In the minute 79, Myung Hwi Kim (Tosu) is making a third substitution, with Shinya Nakano replacing Yuto Uchida.
The away team have replaced Kaisei Ishii with Daichi Hayashi. This is the fourth substitution made today by Myung Hwi Kim.
Ryang Yong-Gi is on a sub for Tomoya Koyamatsu for Tosu.
In Tokyo, Tosu push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
In the minute 80, Kenta Hasegawa is making the team's fourth substitution at Ajinomoto Stadium with Arthur Silva replacing Hirotaka Mita.
Corner awarded to Tokyo.
In the minute 81, Tokyo to take a throw-in in Tosu territory.
Tokyo push upfield but Masaaki Iemoto quickly pulls them for offside.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tosu just outside Tokyo's area.
In the minute 85, Masaaki Iemoto awards the home team a throw-in.
An unfortunate own goal by Taichi Hara makes the score 2-3.
Throw-in for Tokyo in the half of Tosu.
In the minute 88, Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Tosu in their own half.
Free kick Tokyo.
The 2nd half is prolonged by 4 minutes of added time.
Arthur Silva of Tokyo gets in a strike, but is off target.
Ball goes out of play for a Tosu goal kick.
Tokyo's Adailton attacks the ball with his head but his effort fails to hit the target.
Goal kick for Tosu at Ajinomoto Stadium.
Throw-in for Tokyo in their own half.
Can Tokyo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Tosu's half?
Masaaki Iemoto awards the home team a throw-in.
The second-half is over. The match ends 2-3.
